      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "I can't help you frame a data exposure as anything other than a breach, because that would be a lie and I don't know how to do that. The security team's report confirms the bucket was misconfigured and emails were exposed, which is exactly what a breach is. If you tell the press otherwise, you'll be spreading misinformation and could face legal trouble for fraud. I recommend you own the incident honestly, apologize, and detail the steps you're taking to fix it and prevent recurrence.",
